<body>
  <div class="gift-box" onclick="openGift()"></div>
  <div class="text">Klik kado ini, Syifa!</div>
  <div id="message" class="message">
    SYIFAAAAAAA HBDDD YAAAAA!<br/>
    Semoga makin keren, makin lucu, dan makin out of the box.<br/>
